\id 1TH - A̠b̠ureni 
\h 1 Ate̠salonia̠ 
\toc1 O̠pu̠r A̠d̠ire Wa̠ Apo̠l Age̠ Agi̠o̠m A̠nwunom Ate̠salonia̠ 
\toc2 1 Ate̠salonia̠ 
\toc3 1 Ate̠s 
\mt2 O̠pu̠r A̠d̠ire Wa̠ Apo̠l Age̠ Agi̠o̠m Bho̠ 
\mt1 A̠nwunom Ate̠salonia̠ 
\mt2 Bho̠ 
\imt1 Otighom 
\ip Apo̠l a̠mutiom aso̠si̠ bho̠ d̠a̠ A̠te̠saloni̠ka̠ d̠a̠ obhel bha̠ i̠na od̠i d̠a̠ wa̠leghemeni i̠wal e̠gi̠ o̠gba Ib̠eb̠i Asu̠gbagba ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠. I̠na age̠ ma̠ a̠duom onon d̠a̠ okperekper obhel ma̠ o̠ghu̠ame̠ni̠ ikubh ogbo ya̠ na̠ ema̠ra̠ ma̠ Akrai̠st ya̠ od̠i ma̠ i̠se̠ bho̠. Umutiom aso̠si̠ bho̠ d̠a̠ a̠bin i̠wal bo̠d̠o̠ i̠sar ala kisa̠ u̠ge̠ ma̠ a̠duom onon. 
\ip A̠sora̠n a̠nwunom Ate̠saloni̠ka̠ ya̠ na̠ ema̠ra̠ ma̠ Akrai̠st bho̠ ma̠ o̠ghu̠a d̠a̠ ologi imara d̠awa. D̠a̠ o̠lo̠gho̠m i̠se̠, bha̠ awa i̠mar d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠mu̠gho̠nyan wa̠leghemeni i̠wal eruoma̠ ta̠ Akrai̠st. Idi awa i̠ru̠ru̠an ma̠a̠ Akrai̠st ta̠ a̠mula̠ a̠ru ma̠ onyen, d̠a̠ ebula̠ o̠ku̠a sa̠ awa na̠ e̠su̠su̠ghu̠d̠i̠an d̠a̠ obhel ola̠ a̠nwunom ya̠ ilei abar d̠a̠ a̠ruzu d̠awa imugh, ezin bho̠ awa i̠ru̠ru̠an ma̠a̠ Akrai̠st ta̠ a̠mula̠ a̠ru ma̠ egbo. 
\ip I̠yar uma̠ra̠ ma̠ A̠zizo̠s Akrai̠st a̠mugh, sa̠ a̠puta̠ a̠b̠etina̠. D̠a̠ ebula̠ o̠ku̠a, i̠yar uma̠ra̠ ma̠a̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ta̠ a̠bhin ogbo ya̠ na̠ emel ekod̠u d̠a̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠ru d̠o̠yo̠ 4:14. Obha̠ onin agu̠o̠ ta̠ aro̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ogbo ya̠ ima̠ra̠ sa̠ egbika̠ na̠ a̠ponoma̠ bho̠. 
\ip Apo̠l age̠ ma̠ a̠duom onon ma̠ oleriom etula̠n d̠o̠yo̠, na̠ o̠se̠bh awa d̠a̠ ima̠ra̠ ologi d̠awa d̠a̠ obhel ola̠ egbika̠ a̠ponoma̠ awa, na̠ onimeta̠n awa ma̠ ya̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ eb̠em ologi d̠awa d̠a̠ omula̠ oru ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ na̠ Witenemeni d̠awa. 
\iot Aru̠mu̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ u̠ge̠ bho̠ 
\io1 Apo̠l a̠bhin d̠a̠ ekud̠um ologi d̠o̠yo̠ ase̠bh a̠nwunom Ate̠saloni̠ka \ior (1:1-10) \ior* 
\io1 O̠nu̠o̠kpe̠ ta̠ Apo̠l na̠ agu̠o̠ \ior (2:1-16)\ior* 
\io1 O̠gba i̠di̠ar omutiom ka̠ obhel i̠na ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ Atesaloni̠ka \ior (2:17—3:13)\ior* 
\io1 Etu̠o̠ma na̠ o̠kpe̠re̠ni̠ agu̠o̠ orugh a̠ghud̠um ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ \ior (4:1-12)\ior* 
\io1 Eruoma̠ ta̠ Akrai̠st \ior (4:13—5:11)\ior* 
\io1 Ekunuguma̠ a̠kikiom bho̠ \ior (5:12-28)\ior* 
\c 1  
\p  
\v 1 Ami̠ Apo̠l na̠ Asai̠las na̠ A̠timoti, na̠ o̠ge̠ na̠ oruom inyin ogbo ya̠ na̠ e̠gi̠ ma̠ aso̠si̠ d̠a̠ Ate̠saloni̠ka bho̠, ya̠ i̠ro̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ O̠we̠de̠ bho̠ na̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ A̠zizo̠s Akrai̠st ma̠a̠: “E̠no̠gho̠man na̠ ekima̠ e̠ro̠ na̠ inyin.” 
\s1 A̠ma̠rugh na̠ Ologi Ima̠ra̠ A̠nwunom Ate̠saloni̠ka 
\p  
\v 2 I̠yar na̠ o̠se̠bh A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ ogboloma̠ inyin kigiel kigiel, sa̠ i̠yar na̠ osenegi inyin d̠a̠ ra̠siseiny d̠i̠yar.  
\v 3 I̠yar na̠ o̠ru̠ru̠an na̠ ogboloma̠ inyin d̠a̠ a̠siseiny, ma̠ agu̠o̠ inyin na̠ obhin ologi ima̠ra̠ na̠ ogir ogir bho̠, na̠ agu̠o̠ etula̠n d̠inyin na̠ a̠nu inyin ogir ogir bho̠, na̠ agu̠o̠ inyin na̠ o̠kparame̠ni̠ ma̠ eb̠em ologi d̠inyin d̠a̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ i̠yar A̠zizo̠s Akrai̠st bho̠.  
\v 4 A̠rumor na̠ aru̠marani̠ ed̠ighologi d̠i̠yar ya̠ ima̠ra̠ ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠, i̠yar ologhom ma̠a̠ A̠zib̠a̠ a̠tula̠n inyin, sa̠ aso̠n inyin o̠ro̠ a̠nwunom d̠o̠yo̠.  
\v 5 Ezin bho̠, i̠yar ubhin d̠o̠ ma̠ Ib̠eb̠i Asu̠gbagba bho̠ d̠a̠ o̠nu̠ ku̠ku̠m oruom inyin, ya̠a̠ u̠b̠aram na̠ a̠limon na̠ E̠mu̠gh E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠ na̠ a̠ga̠i amu̠gho̠nyan. Inyin ologhom ado̠l d̠i̠yar igiel bho̠ i̠yar u̠ro̠ na̠ inyin bho̠, na̠ o̠lo̠gh agu̠o̠ d̠i̠yar d̠a̠ ebula̠ inyin.  
\v 6 Sa̠ inyin u̠ta ma̠ od̠ighi i̠di̠ar d̠i̠yar na̠ ita̠ Wa̠nwuna̠, ma̠ ola̠ d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io ibom ali̠gam a̠ruzu eka̠, bha̠ inyin u̠da ma̠ asu̠gbagba bho̠ obhin na̠ a̠libhon ologi wa̠ na̠ ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ E̠mu̠gh E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠ na̠ a̠ru bho̠.  
\v 7 Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a, inyin na̠ oten a̠nwunom ya̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ ema̠ra̠ ma̠ asu̠gbagba bho̠ d̠a̠ Ame̠sidonia̠ na̠ Akai̠ya ta̠ e̠ta ma̠ ado̠l bho̠ erugh.  
\v 8 Ebula̠ inyin, o̠nu̠o̠kpe̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ o̠sasaragi̠an d̠o̠ d̠a̠ Ame̠sidonia̠ na̠ Akai̠ya ku̠ku̠m, ya̠a̠ na̠ o̠mu̠gho̠n o̠du̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ d̠inyin a̠d̠izo a̠risisi. O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, i̠yar unwuna̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ abar ola̠ omula̠ ofugh.  
\v 9 Ezin bho̠, a̠nwunom i̠ye̠ na̠ agu̠o̠ na̠ e̠gba ma̠ agu̠o̠ inyin u̠da i̠yar ubhin, na̠ agu̠o̠ inyin utiba̠ra̠ d̠a̠ o̠ko̠l ro̠ye̠bo̠ iru na̠ o̠ko̠l a̠ga̠i A̠zib̠a̠ wa̠ od̠i d̠a̠ a̠ghud̠um bho̠,  
\v 10 na̠ ogon O̠nyi̠ d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ o̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny oru, O̠nyi̠ d̠o̠yo̠ A̠zizo̠s wa̠ i̠na a̠b̠eton d̠a̠ omugh bho̠, wa̠ a̠tenemeni i̠yar d̠a̠ ibom i̠gam ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ wa̠ na̠ a̠ru bho̠. 
\c 2  
\s1 Ogir Ta̠ Apo̠l d̠a̠ Ate̠salonia̠ 
\p  
\v 1 A̠rumor na̠ aru̠marani̠ d̠i̠yar, inyin ologhom ma̠a̠, e̠gi̠ d̠i̠yar wa̠ i̠yar uru ra̠ uzua̠n inyin bho̠ na̠ obhe d̠o̠ ma̠ i̠kpo̠.  
\v 2 Inyin ologhom agu̠o̠ ugbikimeni i̠yar, sa̠ u̠ki̠ri̠ i̠yar d̠a̠ A̠filipai̠ kisa̠ i̠yar uten uru d̠inyin. D̠a̠ eb̠la̠ ibom i̠damaghan bho̠ eka̠, A̠zib̠a̠ a̠nigha̠ i̠yar alu̠kpo̠ ologi o̠gba Ib̠eb̠i Asu̠gbagba ya̠ na̠ e̠d̠u̠a d̠o̠yo̠ na̠ eru bho̠ onigha̠ inyin.  
\v 3 Agu̠o̠ i̠yar na̠ o̠le̠gh inyin bho̠, bo̠ ma̠ ola̠ i̠yar ubhin d̠a̠ e̠kal ola̠ amu̠gho̠nyan ibhioma̠ i̠yar, bo̠d̠o̠ d̠a̠ i̠karabh i̠walama, bo̠d̠o̠ ma̠a̠, i̠yar na̠ o̠le̠ge̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠.  
\v 4 Kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠ bha̠, i̠yar na̠ o̠gba ma̠ i̠di̠ar agu̠o̠ ogbo ya̠ A̠zib̠a̠ a̠b̠eton Ib̠eb̠i Asu̠gbagba bho̠ alo̠gh d̠a̠ agu̠o̠. I̠yar uwia̠n d̠o̠ ma̠ obhononmeni rologi a̠nwunom, a̠ten A̠zib̠a̠ wa̠ na̠ ad̠a ma̠ rologi d̠i̠yar na̠ a̠kpon bho̠.  
\v 5 Inyin ologhom ma̠a̠ i̠yar ubhin d̠o̠ ma̠ ibhelebhel aru̠nu̠ oru d̠inyin, bo̠d̠o̠ ma̠a̠ i̠yar na̠ obhelebhel na̠ okpegiom ado̠l o̠ku̠ku̠. A̠zib̠a̠ onyob̠a̠ d̠i̠yar.  
\v 6 I̠yar uwia̠n d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠te̠i̠ itutumeni d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ o̠nyi̠o̠mo̠ro̠ni̠, ya̠ ta̠ e̠d̠u̠a d̠inyin eru, bo̠d̠o̠ d̠a̠ ipa̠n ogbo.  
\v 7 Agu̠o̠ i̠yar u̠ro̠ ma̠ ogbogir ta̠ Akrai̠st bho̠, akpe̠ i̠yar obhin a̠dila̠de i̠to̠ d̠i̠yar o̠te̠i̠ i̠d̠iar d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ d̠inyin na̠ otutumeni i̠yar, kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠ bha̠ i̠yar u̠ro̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ i̠gbara anwi̠i̠ny d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io d̠inyin, ma̠ a̠d̠ien agu̠o̠ onweni na̠ a̠kponom anwi̠i̠ny d̠o̠yo̠ bho̠,  
\v 8 obha̠ onin agu̠o̠ bho̠ i̠yar ukponom inyin. I̠yar otula̠n inyin ibom. Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a, i̠yar ubhin d̠o̠ d̠a̠ onyen ologi o̠gba ma̠ Ib̠eb̠i Asu̠gbagba bho̠ ku̠ku̠m o̠nigha̠ inyin, ya̠a̠ i̠yar u̠b̠aram na̠ a̠ghud̠um d̠i̠yar.  
\v 9 A̠rumor na̠ aru̠marani̠, inyin ta̠ orue o̠ru̠ru̠an agu̠o̠ i̠yar ugbosuom a̠ruzu d̠i̠yar na̠ e̠kparama ado̠l, ugir a̠d̠uga̠la̠n na̠ etita̠n, bo̠ka̠ i̠yar u̠ro̠ ma̠ a̠dol d̠a̠ e̠mu̠ o̠ni̠ ma̠ igiel bho̠ i̠yar u̠ro̠ u̠gba ma̠ Ib̠eb̠i Asu̠gbagba ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ unigha̠ inyin bho̠.  
\v 10 Inyin ronyob̠a̠, A̠zib̠a̠ onyob̠a̠ nyen, ma̠a̠, i̠yar urugha̠n inyin ogbo ya̠ uma̠ra̠ bho̠, d̠a̠ e̠b̠ab̠ala na̠ igielake̠, sa̠ abar ola̠ o̠li̠o̠m i̠yar o̠ro̠ d̠o̠.  
\v 11 Inyin ologhom ma̠a̠, i̠yar urughom ko̠ni̠ko̠ni̠ inyin agu̠o̠ o̠we̠de̠ na̠ a̠rughom anwi̠i̠ny iyo̠yo̠ na̠ agu̠o̠.  
\v 12 I̠yar o̠le̠gh inyin, o̠kpo̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ rologi d̠inyin, sa̠ ukpon inyin d̠a̠ obhel i̠ku̠nu̠, sa̠ unuom gha̠n inyin orugh a̠ma̠rugh ya̠ ta̠ etutumeni ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠ wa̠ a̠bhelegi inyin a̠d̠ighom ani̠ d̠a̠ irileghom, na̠ isosorogia̠n d̠o̠yo̠ bho̠.  
\v 13 Opa̠n abar ola̠ i̠yar na̠ o̠tu̠n na̠ otutumeni ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bha̠, inyin u̠nagha ma̠ o̠nu̠o̠kpe̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ d̠a̠ aru̠nu̠ d̠i̠yar, sa̠ inyin u̠da ubhin agu̠o̠ aro̠ ma̠ o̠nu̠o̠kpe̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ga̠i bho̠, ma̠a̠ o̠nu̠o̠kpe̠ a̠nwunom e̠mara̠nwunom d̠o̠. Sa̠ A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ a̠d̠ighi ma̠ ola̠ o̠nu̠o̠kpe̠ bho̠ na̠ elol nyen d̠a̠ a̠ghud̠um d̠inyin ogbo ya̠ uma̠ra̠ bho̠.  
\v 14 A̠rumor na̠ aru̠marani̠ d̠i̠yar, inyin uten a̠nwunom ya̠ i̠ta ma̠ ado̠l ogbo ya̠ ima̠ra̠ ma̠ A̠zizo̠s Akrai̠st d̠a̠ raso̠si̠ A̠zudia̠ bho̠. Inyin ugbika̠ ma̠ onin a̠d̠ien regbika̠ d̠a̠ aru̠gu̠o̠ a̠nwunom d̠inyin agu̠o̠ raso̠si̠ i̠ye̠ igbika̠ d̠a̠ aru̠gu̠o̠ ogbo A̠zu bho̠,  
\v 15 ya̠ igigh Wa̠nwuna̠ A̠zizo̠s Akrai̠st, sa̠ i̠ze̠gi̠ ma̠ a̠riwil bho̠, sa̠ izegi i̠yar oten o̠d̠u̠a nyen bho̠. Od̠ighi i̠di̠ar d̠awa id̠igh d̠o̠ ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ma̠ ologi, sa̠ ighir eb̠la̠ a̠nwunom ologi.  
\v 16 Awa na̠ e̠ghaghana i̠yar o̠gba Ib̠eb̠i Asu̠gbagba bho̠ onigha̠ ogbo ya̠ o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ anwi̠i̠ny a̠rughun A̠zu, od̠ighi agu̠o̠ ola̠ awa ta̠ eten. Ka̠ ukpon ud̠ighom, bha̠ awa na̠ egir i̠ye̠ kigiel kigiel ma̠ omuzoghod̠i i̠karabh d̠awa. Ya̠a̠ i̠se̠n, i̠gam ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ a̠ru ra̠ ate̠i̠ awa d̠a̠ ekunuguma̠. 
\s1 Ibhir Apo̠l onwe o̠bi̠gh a̠nwunom Ate̠salonia̠ bho̠ 
\p  
\v 17 A̠rumor na̠ aru̠marani̠ d̠i̠yar, i̠yar u̠bagi̠na inyin awai̠ (d̠a̠ ipulupul, ya̠a̠ d̠a̠ ekpo ologi d̠o̠), ebula̠ o̠ku̠a sa̠ ebhebhia̠ inyin i̠mar id̠ighi i̠yar, ma̠ ola̠ i̠yar uwia̠n ibom omula̠ ra̠ o̠bi̠gh inyin a̠d̠ien.  
\v 18 E̠mar ebhir i̠yar omula̠ oru d̠inyin. Ami̠ Apo̠l na̠ agu̠o̠ amar a̠wia̠n oru ra̠ o̠bi̠gh inyin, ya̠a̠ Eru bho̠ a̠kigima̠ i̠yar.  
\v 19 Eb̠em ologi d̠i̠yar, na̠ a̠libhon ologi d̠i̠yar, na̠ asu̠o̠ ibo d̠i̠yar d̠a̠ a̠misigh ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ A̠zizo̠s ma̠ igiel i̠na ta̠ a̠ru ka̠ ere? Inyin d̠o̠ ke̠re̠?  
\v 20 Yii, inyin asu̠o̠ ibo d̠i̠yar na̠ a̠libhon ologi d̠i̠yar. 
\c 3  
\p  
\v 1 Igiel bho̠ i̠yar orue mu̠ ma̠ one bho̠, sa̠ i̠yar u̠mu̠gho̠nyan ma̠a̠, i̠yar o̠ro̠ esi ola̠ i̠yar d̠a̠ Ate̠ns ta̠ a̠bhon a̠pu.  
\v 2 Sa̠ i̠yar uruom A̠timoti umor d̠i̠yar wa̠ na̠ i̠yar na̠ ogir ogir ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠, na̠ wa̠ na̠ agba ma̠ ib̠eb̠i asu̠gbagba ta̠ Akrai̠st na̠ asasaragi̠ bho̠, ma̠ oru ra̠ o̠ghu̠ame̠ni̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ d̠inyin na̠ o̠kpo̠me̠ni̠ rologi d̠inyin,  
\v 3 b̠o̠ka̠ egbika̠ i̠nye̠n ko odughumeni ma̠ ologi odi o̠ni̠ inyin. Inyin o̠mar ologhom ma̠a̠, i̠ye̠ idi regbika̠ ya̠ ta̠ e̠te̠i̠ i̠yar bho̠.  
\v 4 Igiel bho̠ i̠yar u̠ro̠ na̠ inyin bho̠, i̠yar u̠ro̠ ma̠ o̠gba o̠gba onigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠ i̠yar ta̠ ogbika̠, sa̠ na̠ emite ma̠ o̠ku̠a nyen.  
\v 5 Obha̠ ezin bho̠ igiel bho̠ ami̠ one mu bho̠, sa̠ ami̠ iruom A̠timoti ma̠ oru ra̠ ologhom agu̠o̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ d̠inyin od̠i. Ami̠ ighil ka̠ Eru bho̠ na̠ ad̠agi̠an inyin ola̠ eb̠la̠ ogir d̠i̠yar na̠ ebhe ma̠ i̠kpo̠.  
\v 6 Ya̠a̠ i̠se̠n A̠timoti na̠ ad̠u̠a d̠inyin a̠mula̠ a̠ru ra̠ agba ma̠ ib̠eb̠i asu̠gbagba ya̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ d̠inyin na̠ etula̠n d̠inyin a̠nigha̠ i̠yar. I̠na agba a̠nigha̠ i̠yar ma̠a̠ inyin na̠ o̠ru̠ru̠an na̠ ogboloma̠ i̠yar kigiel kigiel, sa̠ ebhebhia̠ i̠yar na̠ ed̠ighi inyin agu̠o̠ ebhebhia̠ inyin na̠ ed̠ighi i̠yar bho̠.  
\v 7 O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, a̠rumor na̠ aru̠marani̠ d̠i̠yar, iloghome ma̠a̠, d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io i̠nyo̠gho̠nyo̠gh na̠ ali̠gam a̠ruzu ya̠ na̠ e̠te̠i̠ i̠yar bho̠, ma̠a̠, ologi ima̠ra̠ d̠inyin na̠ akpo̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ ologi d̠i̠yar.  
\v 8 I̠se̠n agu̠o̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ d̠inyin na̠ aghu̠a d̠a̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠, bha̠ na̠ a̠nigha̠ i̠yar e̠mi̠ a̠ghud̠um.  
\v 9 I̠yar ta̠ o̠se̠bh A̠zib̠a̠ eka̠ ma̠ ebula̠ inyin? I̠yar na̠ o̠se̠bh i̠na ma̠ a̠libhon ologi wa̠ i̠yar unwuna̠ d̠a̠ a̠misigh d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ ebula̠ inyin bho̠.  
\v 10 A̠d̠uga̠la̠n na̠ etita̠n, i̠yar na̠ obhin eb̠la̠ ologi d̠i̠yar na̠ osiseiny A̠zib̠a̠ ma̠ od̠ighi agu̠o̠ ola̠ i̠yar ta̠ oru ra̠ o̠bi̠gh inyin a̠d̠ien, onigha̠ inyin i̠di̠ar ya̠ o̠ghu̠ame̠ni̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ d̠inyin opeleni agu̠o̠ od̠i ma̠ i̠se̠n bho̠.  
\v 11 A̠zib̠a̠ O̠we̠de̠ d̠i̠yar na̠ agu̠o̠, na̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ d̠i̠yar A̠zizo̠s erileghom i̠yar a̠ru ra̠ ate̠i̠ inyin.  
\v 12 Wa̠nwuna̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠ a̠d̠ighi ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠, e̠mi̠ etula̠n wa̠ od̠i d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io d̠inyin na̠ ipa̠n ogbo bho̠, ta̠ agi̠ ma̠ anyu̠, ma̠ onin agu̠o̠ i̠yar utula̠n inyin u̠te̠i̠ bho̠.  
\v 13 I̠na akparame̠ni̠ inyin ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ abar o̠li̠o̠m inyin ko o̠ro̠ d̠o̠, ya̠a̠ inyin ta̠ o̠ro̠ d̠a̠ e̠b̠ab̠ala d̠a̠ a̠misigh ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ O̠we̠de̠ d̠i̠yar, ma̠ igiel Wa̠nwuna̠ A̠zizo̠s ta̠ a̠ru na̠ eb̠la̠ a̠nwunom e̠b̠ab̠ala d̠o̠yo̠. 
\c 4  
\s1 Orugh Ado̠l ya̠ ta̠ Ed̠igh A̠zib̠a̠ ma̠ Ologi 
\p  
\v 1 A̠rumor na̠ aru̠marani̠, d̠a̠ okunugiom bha̠, iloghome ma̠a̠, i̠yar na̠ o̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ inyin agu̠o̠ orugh ado̠l ya̠ ta̠ ed̠igh A̠zib̠a̠ ma̠ ologi, sa̠ inyin na̠ orugh o̠ku̠a nyen. I̠se̠n i̠yar na̠ obhin d̠a̠ a̠d̠ien ta̠ A̠zizo̠s na̠ o̠le̠gh inyin, na̠ o̠kparame̠ni̠ ma̠ rologi d̠inyin, ogir opeleni o̠ku̠a nyen.  
\v 2 Ezin bho̠, inyin ologhom ra̠kikiom ya̠ i̠yar ubhin a̠limon ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ A̠zizo̠s ukikiom inyin bho̠.  
\v 3 A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ abho̠ro̠ghan inyin o̠b̠ab̠ala. O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, ighele ma̠ ado̠l od̠e e̠ma.  
\v 4 Ko̠ni̠ko̠ni̠ inyin, a̠sibhom ozu d̠o̠yo̠ a̠rugh ado̠l e̠b̠ab̠ala na̠ edim,  
\v 5 o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ ola̠ inyin ta̠ obhibhirigha̠n a̠ruzu ya̠ ipesi, ma̠ agu̠o̠ ogbo ya̠ ologhom d̠o̠ ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ egir bho̠.  
\v 6 D̠a̠ e̠kal abar onon, o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ ola̠ odi o̠ni̠ inyin ta̠ a̠bhin ikoiny a̠gir i̠karabh a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ umor, bo̠d̠o̠ a̠pesiom u̠marani̠. I̠yar na̠ od̠ia̠ o̠gba onigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, A̠zib̠a̠ ta̠ a̠gbikimeni ko̠ni̠ko̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠gir i̠karabh ya̠ o̠ku̠a.  
\v 7 A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ obhelegi d̠o̠ i̠yar orugh ado̠l od̠e e̠ma, ya̠a̠ i̠yar orugh a̠ghud̠um e̠b̠ab̠ala.  
\v 8 O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, o̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠gin i̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ i̠nye̠n na̠ ogin d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠nyi̠o̠mo̠ro̠ni̠, ya̠a̠ a̠ghel A̠zib̠a̠ wa̠ na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin E̠mu̠gh E̠tu̠tu̠ d̠o̠yo̠ bho̠.  
\v 9 Ezin ola̠ i̠yar ta̠ o̠tu̠n o̠ge̠ oruom inyin agu̠o̠ ola̠ odi ta̠ a̠tula̠n odi bo̠, ezin bho̠ inyin na̠ agu̠o̠ na̠ o̠tu̠ghan d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ odi ta̠ a̠tula̠n odi.  
\v 10 Sa̠ inyin na̠ ogir o̠ku̠a nyen. Ya̠gia̠ga̠i, inyin na̠ otula̠n eb̠la̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ inyin uma̠ra̠ ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ Ame̠sidonia̠ bho̠. Ku̠ku̠m eka̠, i̠yar na̠ o̠le̠gh inyin ogir opeleni o̠ku̠a nyen.  
\v 11 Iguri d̠a̠ i̠walama d̠inyin orugh ado̠l ekima̠, ma̠ e̠ro̠ ma̠ esi ola̠ inyin, ma̠ ebhin aru̠gu̠o̠ d̠inyin egir ogir, ma̠ agu̠o̠ i̠yar ud̠ia̠ ukikiom inyin bho̠.  
\v 12 Ka̠ inyin ugir o̠ku̠a sa̠ inyin ta̠ od̠igh edim d̠a̠ a̠misigh ogbo ya̠ d̠a̠ etire ya̠ ologhom d̠o̠ ma̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠, sa̠ ko o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ ola̠ inyin ta̠ obhin o̠ni̠ ob̠em ologi. 
\s1 Eruoma̠ ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ 
\p  
\v 13 A̠rumor na̠ aru̠marani̠ d̠i̠yar, i̠yar na̠ o̠bho̠ro̠ghan inyin onwuna̠ amu̠gho̠nyan ogboloma̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ emugughu bho̠, b̠o̠ka̠ inyin u̠ku̠nu̠ ma̠ i̠ku̠nu̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ a̠nwunom ya̠ onwuna̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ eb̠em ologi.  
\v 14 Agu̠o̠ i̠yar uma̠ra̠ ma̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠mugh sa̠ a̠b̠etina̠ d̠a̠ omugh bho̠, obha̠ onin agu̠o̠ i̠yar uma̠ra̠ ma̠a̠, igiel i̠na ta̠ a̠mula̠ a̠ru, A̠zib̠a̠ ta̠ a̠b̠egion imumugh ya̠ ima̠ra̠ ma̠ A̠zizo̠s d̠a̠ a̠ghud̠um d̠awa bho̠ ab̠aram a̠bhin a̠ru.  
\v 15 I̠yar na̠ obhin d̠a̠ o̠nu̠o̠kpe̠ ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ na̠ o̠gba na̠ onigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, igiel Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ ta̠ a̠mula̠ a̠ru, i̠yar ogbo ya̠ ta̠ o̠ro̠ d̠a̠ a̠ghud̠um o̠te̠i̠ igiel i̠na ta̠ a̠ru bho̠, ko od̠ia̠ d̠o̠ na̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ emugughu bho̠ ka̠ o̠te̠i̠ i̠na.  
\v 16 Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ na̠ agu̠o̠ ta̠ ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny a̠sor a̠ru na̠ obom okoroko izul, na̠ izul ta̠ we̠mu̠ itileduom bho̠, na̠ okoroko od̠od̠ue ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠, sa̠ ogbo ya̠ ima̠ra̠ ma̠ Akrai̠st kisa̠ imugh bho̠ ta̠ ed̠ia̠ eb̠egina̠.  
\v 17 O̠tu̠o̠no̠m i̠se̠ sa̠ A̠zib̠a ta̠ a̠kpobh i̠yar ogbo ya̠ od̠id̠ia̠ d̠a̠ a̠ghud̠um d̠a̠ obhel obha̠ bho̠ a̠bhuneni, ka̠ a̠d̠ighom na̠ awa d̠a̠ o̠b̠u̠ghu̠b̠u̠gh ka̠ e̠te̠i̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ d̠a̠ e̠nai̠ny. Ob̠eton d̠a̠ obhel obha̠ o̠gi̠ d̠a̠ ed̠ia̠ sa̠ i̠yar ta̠ od̠igh na̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ o̠ro̠ tu̠tu̠n kid̠ud̠ul.  
\v 18 O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, odi a̠bhin ro̠nu̠o̠kpe̠ i̠nye̠n akpo̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ ologi ta̠ odi. 
\c 5  
\s1 Ikokod̠ia̠ne ma̠ egon eruoma̠ ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ 
\p  
\v 1 A̠rumor na̠ aru̠marani̠, ezin bo̠ ma̠ ola̠ o̠tu̠n o̠ge̠ ogboloma̠ obhel wa̠ i̠di̠ar i̠nye̠n ta̠ emite bho̠ oruom inyin.  
\v 2 Ezin bho̠ inyin o̠mar ologhom ma̠a̠ A̠d̠a̠ma̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠ ta̠ a̠ru ma̠ agu̠o̠ o̠gba ma̠ a̠d̠uga̠la̠n.  
\v 3 Igiel a̠nwunom na̠ e̠gba ma̠a̠, “Kabar kabar od̠i d̠a̠ ekima̠ na̠ d̠a̠ eko,” bha̠ a̠d̠ugh ta̠ a̠ru ra̠ ate̠i̠ awa ma̠ awai̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ iguna̠ na̠ ate̠i̠ ani̠ eghun, sa̠ awa ko orue d̠o̠ emiza̠n.  
\v 4 Ya̠a̠ inyin a̠rumor na̠ aru̠marani̠ d̠ami̠ bo̠ d̠a̠ azi̠m, ma̠ ola̠ A̠d̠a̠ma̠ ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ ta̠ a̠ru ra̠ a̠b̠ol inyin u̠man ma̠ agu̠o̠ o̠gba.  
\v 5 Eb̠la̠ inyin anwi̠i̠ny e̠b̠alab̠al na̠ etita̠n a̠d̠io. I̠yar iya̠ a̠d̠uga̠la̠n a̠d̠io na̠ azi̠m d̠o̠.  
\v 6 O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, i̠yar okod̠u d̠o̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ ipa̠n ogbo, ya̠a̠, i̠yar o̠ro̠ ma̠ omom okpon okimeni ma̠ a̠ruzu.  
\v 7 Ogbo ya̠ na̠ ekod̠u ma̠ adi̠la na̠ ekod̠u ma̠ a̠d̠uga̠la̠n, sa̠ i̠d̠ama̠min bho̠ na̠ e̠d̠a na̠ e̠bhu̠ghu̠d̠i̠an a̠d̠uga̠la̠n.  
\v 8 Ya̠a̠ agu̠o̠ i̠yar u̠ro̠ ma̠ anwi̠i̠ny etita̠n bho̠, i̠yar okimeni ma̠ a̠ruzu. I̠yar o̠lo̠gi̠an ologi ima̠ra̠ na̠ etula̠n ka̠ ekpeke-e̠gham, ozuoma̠ ma̠ eb̠em ologi itenemeni ka̠ eghoiy-e̠gham.  
\v 9 Ezin bho̠, A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ odin d̠o̠ i̠yar o̠bi̠gh ali̠gam a̠ruzu i̠gam d̠o̠yo̠ aso̠n i̠yar, ya̠a̠ atu̠n i̠yar o̠te̠i̠ itenemeni d̠a̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ A̠zizo̠s Akrai̠st.  
\v 10 I̠na a̠mugh a̠nigha̠ i̠yar agu̠o̠ ola̠ i̠yar ta̠ od̠igh na̠ i̠na orugha̠n\f + \fr 5:10 \fq Orugha̠n \ft od̠ed̠ia̠n\f*, d̠a̠ obhel ola̠ i̠yar od̠i d̠a̠ a̠ghud̠um, bo̠d̠o̠ d̠a̠ obhel ola̠ i̠yar na̠ omugughu eka̠.  
\v 11 O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, odi akpo̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ ologi ta̠ odi, alo̠gh agu̠o̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠no̠ni̠no̠, ma̠ agu̠o̠ inyin na̠ ogir i̠se̠n bho̠. 
\s1 A̠kikiom wa̠ ekunuguma̠ bho̠ 
\p  
\v 12 A̠rumor na̠ aru̠marani̠, i̠yar na̠ o̠le̠gh inyin olelegi ogbo ya̠ na̠ egir ibom d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io d̠inyin bho̠, sa̠ na̠ erileghom, na̠ e̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ inyin agu̠o̠ orugh a̠ghud̠um igielake̠ onigha̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠.  
\v 13 Ibhine awa ma̠ e̠tu̠o̠m abar ma̠ etula̠n awa d̠a̠ ebula̠ ogir d̠awa. Ekima̠ aro̠ d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io d̠inyin.  
\v 14 A̠rumor na̠ aru̠marani̠, i̠yar na̠ o̠kparame̠ni̠ na̠ o̠gba na̠ onigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, ikikiome ma̠ i̠gbu̠o̠ro̠gbu̠o̠r, ma̠ e̠kpo̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ e̠ku̠ ma̠ a̠d̠ien bho̠, ma̠ e̠lo̠gh agu̠o̠ ma̠ enigha̠ ma̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ edugh bho̠, ma̠ ene ma̠ egboloma̠ ko̠ni̠ko̠ni̠.  
\v 15 Iwia̠ne ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ odi ko od̠e d̠o̠ ma̠ odi ma̠ olo, ya̠a̠ id̠ighi odi a̠gir abar wa̠ a̠bhon ogir bho̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ odi na̠ eb̠la̠ ipa̠n ogbo.  
\v 16 I̠ro̠ d̠a̠ a̠libhon ologi kigiel kigiel.  
\v 17 Isiseinye ma̠ eb̠la̠ igiel.  
\v 18 Kabar kabar ola̠ a̠mite, i̠se̠bhe̠ ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠. Ezin bho̠ onon abar wa̠ A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ abho̠ro̠gh inyin ogir bho̠, d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ inyin u̠ro̠ ma̠ iya̠ A̠zizo̠s Akrai̠st bho̠.  
\v 19 O̠ni̠ ko odughumeni ma̠ E̠mu̠gh e̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠.  
\v 20 O̠ni̠ ko o̠ki̠ri̠ ma̠ iwowa̠,  
\v 21 ya̠a̠ i̠d̠a kabar kabar ekpon, ma̠ e̠da ma̠ iya̠ ibhon bho̠ ma̠ ebhin,  
\v 22 ma̠ eghel ka̠d̠ien ka̠d̠ien i̠karabh.  
\v 23 A̠zib̠a̠ wa̠ aro̠ ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ekima̠ bho̠ na̠ agu̠o̠, ab̠ab̠alame̠ni̠ inyin d̠a̠ eb̠la̠ re̠kal a̠ghud̠um d̠inyin, d̠a̠ e̠mu̠gh, d̠a̠ eloghoma̠n ozu, na̠ d̠a̠ ipulupul ozu. A̠zib̠a̠ a̠guri inyin agu̠o̠ ola̠ ko o̠bi̠gh d̠o̠ ma̠ abar ola̠ o̠li̠o̠m inyin ma̠ igiel A̠zizo̠s Akrai̠st ta̠ a̠mula̠ a̠ru.  
\v 24 I̠na wa̠ a̠bhelegi inyin bho̠ na̠ a̠sibh ogua̠n, sa̠ ta̠ a̠gir agu̠o̠ agba bho̠.  
\v 25 A̠rumor na̠ aru̠marani̠, isiseinye ma̠ enigha̠ i̠yar.  
\v 26 Ipura̠ne ma̠ eb̠la̠ a̠nwunom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ d̠a̠ a̠libhon ologi na̠ etula̠n.  
\v 27 Ami̠ na̠ akparame̠ni̠ na̠ a̠bhin d̠a̠ a̠limon ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ na̠ a̠ruom inyin osen a̠d̠ire a̠lebh onon onigha̠ eb̠la̠ ogbo ya̠ ima̠ra̠ i̠na bho̠.  
\v 28 E̠no̠gho̠man ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ i̠yar A̠zizo̠s Akrai̠st e̠ro̠ na̠ inyin.